 Reports just reaching New Telegraph indicate that a gas plant, located in the Baruwa area of Lagos, is currently on fire.
Although reports are still sketchy, it was learnt that an explosion was heard at the plant around 6 this morning.
Officials of the Lagos State Emergency Management Agency (LASEMA) have mobilised to the scene.
